<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Beautiful Cards with Gaps</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <style>
        .card-group {
            margin: 2rem auto;
            max-width: 90%;
        }

        .card {
            border: 1px solid #921d21;
            /* Border matching primary color */
            border-radius: 15px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            /* Slight zoom on hover */
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            /* Subtle shadow effect */
        }

        .card-title {
            color: #921d21;
            /* Primary color for titles */
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .card-footer {
            background-color: #921d21;
            color: #fff;
            /* White text on footer */
        }

        .card-footer small {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .card-text {
            color: #555;
            /* Slightly muted text */
        }

        .card-group .card:not(:last-child) {
            margin-right: 1rem;
            /* Add spacing between cards */
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .card-group .card:not(:last-child) {
                margin-right: 0;
                /* Remove spacing for smaller screens */
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
                /* Add vertical spacing for smaller screens */
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="card-group">
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="/images/cards1.jpeg" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Main Campus Srikakulam</h5>
                <p class="card-text">

                    The Main Campus Srikakulam Mess offers a vibrant and well-organized dining experience for students
                    and staff. Located at the heart of the campus, it provides a variety of nutritious, freshly prepared
                    meals catering to different tastes and dietary preferences. With a focus on quality and hygiene, the
                    mess ensures that every meal is served in a clean, welcoming environment. It plays an integral role
                    in the daily life of students, offering not just food, but a space to relax, socialize, and enjoy a
                    sense of community. The Main Campus Srikakulam Mess is committed to providing a comfortable,
                    satisfying, and wholesome dining experience for all. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <small>Last updated 3 mins ago</small>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="/images/cards2.jpeg" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Mini Campus in Shivani</h5>
                <p class="card-text">

                    The IIIT (Indian Institute of Information Technology) main campus in Srikakulam offers a
                    well-maintained mess facility that provides nutritious and hygienic food to its students and staff.
                    The mess serves a variety of meals, catering to diverse tastes and dietary preferences, including
                    vegetarian and non-vegetarian options. The focus is on providing balanced, wholesome meals that
                    support students' academic and extracurricular activities. With a clean and comfortable dining
                    environment, the mess ensures a pleasant and satisfying dining experience, promoting the well-being
                    of the campus community. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <small>Last updated 3 mins ago</small>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="/images/cards1.jpeg" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Campus-3 in Nuzvid</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    The IIIT Main Campus in Nuzvid is known for its well-equipped infrastructure and a vibrant academic
                    environment. The campus features a student-friendly mess that serves a variety of nutritious and
                    delicious meals to cater to the diverse tastes and dietary preferences of its students. The mess
                    focuses on providing balanced meals that promote health and well-being, ensuring students have
                    access to quality food that supports their demanding schedules. With a clean and hygienic
                    environment, the mess fosters a communal atmosphere where students can socialize and relax while
                    enjoying their meals. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <small>Last updated 3 mins ago</small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>